ğŸ–¼ï¸ Image Classification with Hugging Face Transformers
This project demonstrates how to fine-tune state-of-the-art image classification models (like ViT, ResNet, ConvNeXT, and Swin Transformer) using the Hugging Face ğŸ¤— Transformers library and PyTorch. It supports training with both the Trainer API and a custom training loop using Accelerate.

